text: Kelsey Snook is speaking at Creative Mornings next week. Her company, Daily Tous les Jours, does really interesting participatory design projects. <http://creativemornings.com/talks/kelsey-snook>

I'm getting a group of people together to talk about motion and how we want to think about it moving forward. I'm hoping to pin down the outlines of a gameplan on how we use motion in the future, cross-department collaboration is going to be a big part of the discussion I think. It's mostly devs I know have done motion work at this point but anyone can come if they want.
